OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly dry with sunny spells on
OL,6,FMonday morning, although isolated
OL,7,Fshowers possible at first in the
OL,8,Fnorth. Cloud thickening early
OL,9,Fafternoon, with outbreaks of rain
OL,10,Fspreading east. Strong and gusty winds
OL,11,Feasing. Mild, but feeling cooler in
OL,12,Fthe wind.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,15,Fthis evening, but this slowly easing
OL,16,Fto become largely dry by dawn, perhaps
OL,17,Fwith some clear spells. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
