OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FMostly dry Tuesday with some
OL,6,Fsunny spells. Cloud clearing later in
OL,7,Fthe afternoon to give longer sunny
OL,8,Fspells. Mild.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FEarly
OL,11,Ffog clearing then mostly dry but often
OL,12,Fcloudy Wednesday. Very mild. Breezy
OL,13,Fwith rain or showers Thursday. Mild.
OL,14,FFriday likely wet and windy at first,
OL,15,Fthen cooler with showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
